{"tid":528462,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過遇上對的人，但係一個錯既時候？","createTime":"2018-01-13T19:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T11:14:02.000Z","uid":24196,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c49e3f192a24e40502cfc931b6bc2cbcd9d8d765","tid":528462,"uid":24196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已分手，自己都有新既另一半<br />\n分手初期好憎佢，因為一齊既時候比左好多機會佢<br />\n但一次又一次地傷害我<br />\n到最後用哂所謂既限額時，佢喊住同我講會改，想復合，但當時我過唔到自己個關，最後都係拒絕左佢<br />\n<br />\n其實對佢都已經冇愛，但只覺得好可惜，因為大家都好夾<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們深夜擺低你既 「可惜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 我好愛現任女朋友"},{"pid":"37c96bffc201a09fe19d95e4cb8bd76fd6a4b004","tid":528462,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:27:06.000Z","msg":"咩係冇愛 咩係限額"},{"pid":"c69fa718b71da88a3c0bea136737ed716c3415ba","tid":528462,"uid":127727,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"37c96bffc201a09fe19d95e4cb8bd76fd6a4b004","tid":528462,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:27:06.000Z","msg":"咩係冇愛 咩係限額"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:28:17.000Z","msg":"藉口"},{"pid":"44579ad4141b542b47f5b90f199da3f203258695","tid":528462,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩係冇愛 咩係限額</blockquote>藉口</blockquote><br />\n完"},{"pid":"6652db098a8ce106f64d2d742e62e3dc1bc09e8c","tid":528462,"uid":24196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"37c96bffc201a09fe19d95e4cb8bd76fd6a4b004","tid":528462,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:27:06.000Z","msg":"咩係冇愛 咩係限額"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:31:01.000Z","msg":"宜家有時候工作場合都會見到佢，又冇憎既感覺，但硬係完全唔想同佢有交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為一齊個陣佢發脾氣，撩鬧交既次數都比較多<br />\n起初覺得忍讓下冇所謂，但慢慢佢就有雙重標準<br />\n無形之